{"view":"article","slug":"star-pyraminx","category":"Non-WCA","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Non-WCA","title":{"en":"六角星金字塔"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>六角星金字塔</strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>Yujian Song (宋雨键)</p><p>2019/10/15</p><p>六角星金字塔是蓝蓝在今年九月量产的一款异形, 外形为正四面体, 但却有12个旋转轴, 每一步转动都是jumble, 与传统的金字塔截然不同, 也与菱12轴的直升机有很大的区别, 是一款很有意思的魔方. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image2.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>六角星金字塔, 图源阿里巴巴</p><p>六角星金字塔与Seth Holiday在17年的作品Clover Tetrahedron十分相似, 而蓝蓝选择的切割更为美观一些. 这个Clover Tetrahedron的名称也是十分贴切, 因为它正好是正四面体版本的三叶草: (下图是Clover Tetrahedron和一些其他的三叶草魔方)</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image3.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image4.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image5.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image6.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>从左到右Clover Tetrahedron, Trifurcation Cube, Clover Octahedron, Clover Dodecahedron, 图源TwistyPuzzles</p><p>(其中Clover Cube因与奇艺魔方格的四叶草重名而改称Trifurcation Cube)</p><p>下图的4 Corners Cube是六角星金字塔的一个同构变形, 在4 Corners Cube的基础上继续切割就得到了大雁的比翼鸟和双飞燕. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image7.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>4 Corners Cube, 图源TwistyPuzzles</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image8.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image9.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>大雁比翼鸟, 双飞燕, 图源阿里巴巴</p><p>和其他的三叶草魔方一样, 六芒星金字塔的每一步转动都是jumble, 为了更好地研究它的解法, 我们需要分析清楚它的转动. </p><p>六角星金字塔的每条棱上有两个旋转轴, 旋转方式如图所示: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image10.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>ur棱上方的旋转轴转一定角度时, ul棱上方将可以进行jumble旋转; 而继续旋转ur棱上方的轴, 可以使ur棱下方进行jumble旋转. </p><p>我们来看一下这个魔方旋转轴的分布: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image11.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image12.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>可以看到有12个轴, 但是不同于正12轴或是菱12轴, 每个轴的反向延长不再是旋转轴, 也就是说没有彼此平行的旋转面. 每个旋转轴周围不均匀地分布着三个轴, 且容易算出相邻两个轴的夹角大小为<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image13.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">. </p><p>现在我们将整个魔方的切割移到球面上, 如同在分析直升机魔方的jumble时做的那样: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image14.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image16.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>可以看到每个圆内有三道切割, 旋转一个轴, 只要对齐切割, 相邻的旋转轴就可以继续旋转.旋转角<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image17.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">当然是第一个旋转面截相邻两个旋转面截成的角, 按照前图所画的旋转方式, 两个旋转面所成二面角为<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image18.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 故用三面角余弦定理不难算出<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image19.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">. <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image20.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">是一个无理数, 这说明我们确实遇到了jumble. </p><p>相距较远的两道切割的旋转角<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image21.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">.<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image22.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">也是一个无理数, 说明六角星金字塔的任意旋转都会产生jumble. </p><p>接下来我们研究它的解法, 先做一些转动规定. </p><p><strong>转动规定</strong></p><p>用L,R,U,B四个字母指代四个方向, 两个字母组合代表相应的棱, 且靠前的字母代表靠近轴靠近该方向, 用”+”,”-“代表顺时针或逆时针旋转<a id=\"MTBlankEqn\"></a><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image23.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 用”+ +”,”- -”代表顺时针或逆时针旋转<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image24.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 例如:</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image25.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image26.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image27.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image28.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>UR +</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>UR - -</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>RU -</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>UR - UL + +</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>注意这并不代表<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image29.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">是<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image30.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">的两倍, 事实上<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image31.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 有一定的理由将旋转<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image29.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">作为基准记”+”, 旋转<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image32.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">则应记”- -”, 但这样会使得顺时针逆时针发生混乱, 且小角度被记为两次旋转, 故不采用这种记法. </p><p><strong>第一步: 复形</strong></p><p>尽管六角星金字塔的每一步转动都会产生jumble, 但我们复原的第一步仍然是复形, 复形之后可以通过叠加jumble转动来得到使魔方形状保持不变的公式. </p><p>我们注意到每个旋转轴上都有一个中心块, 即下图中橙色标出的块. 在旋转UR轴时, 其只会绕轴旋转, 并且不受其他旋转轴的影响, 位置始终保持不变. 我们复形时, 可以先将所有的此类中心块位置调正(可能需要简单处理一些jumble造成的捆绑), 再进行下一步操作. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image33.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>另一个这样做的理由是这个魔方的角块加一个单色块与一个棱块等效, 这点从球面上的切割很容易看出, 同时可以看出等效之后的三循环, 在摆正中心块后可以用三循环进行复形. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image34.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image35.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>例如做set up <strong>RU - -</strong>, 可以对如下三个位置进行交换: <strong>UR - - UB + + UR + + UB - -</strong>, 再reverse <strong>RU + +</strong>. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image36.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image37.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image38.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>逆序可得如下复形公式: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image39.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>RU - - UB + + UR - - UB - - UR + + RU + +</strong></p><p>同样: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image40.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>RU - - UR - - UB + + UR + + UB - - RU + +</strong></p><p>还有下面一些公式: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image41.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UL + + LU + + UL + + UB - - UL - - UB + + UL - - LU - -</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image42.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>RB + UR + + RU + + RB - RU - - UR - -</strong></p><p>调整错位块的位置: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image43.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image44.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UL - - UR + + UL + + UR - -</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image45.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image46.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UR - - RU + + UR + + RU - -</strong></p><p>如下情况可以逐步转化: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image47.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image48.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image49.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image50.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image51.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>故而有公式: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image47.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>BU - - BR + + BU + + BR - - BL + + BR - - BL - - BR - RB - - BR - - RB + + LB + + UL - -</strong> <strong>LU + + UL + + LU - - LB - -</strong></p><p>单一个错位角块可以先通过三循环转化为上图情况, 于是可以复原: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image52.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image47.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UL + + UB - - UL - - UB + +</strong></p><p>用这些方法可以完成复形. </p><p><strong>第二步: 复原棱块</strong></p><p>利用我们之前的三循环, 为了使魔方的形状不再变化, 可以先set up将三个位置全变成棱块, 例如做<strong>UL - - RL + +</strong>: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image53.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image54.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>接下来可做橙色标记位置的三循环, 整理出以下公式(逆向逆序): </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image55.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UL - - RL + + RU + + UR - - RU - - UR + + RL - - UL + +</strong></p><p>或者做set up <strong>UR - - UB + + UR - - UB - - UR -</strong>: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image56.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image57.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>有三循环: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image58.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UR - - UB + + UR - - UB - - UR - UR + + UL - - UR - - UL + + UR + UB + + UR + + UB - -</strong> <strong>UR + +</strong></p><p>通过改变方向叠加该公式可得两棱翻: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image59.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UR - - UB + + UR - - UB - - UR - UR + + UL - - UR - - UL + + UR + UB + + UR + + UB - -</strong> <strong>UR + + UL + + UB - - UL + + UB + + UL + UL - - UR + + UL + + UR - - UL - UB - - UL - -</strong> <strong>UB + + UL - -</strong></p><p>另外棱块可能出现两块对换, 这时角块也必定为奇置换, 类似三阶魔方奇偶校验, 可以通过叠加”棱-角-棱”与”角-棱-角”三循环处理: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image60.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UL - - UR + + UL + + UR + RU + + UR + + RU - -</strong></p><p>至此棱块完成. </p><p><strong>第三步: 复原角块</strong></p><p>与复原棱块时类似, 同样可以通过set up来寻找三角换, 例如做<strong>RU + + LU - -</strong>: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image61.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image62.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>得到三循环: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image63.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>RU + + LU - - UL - - UR + + UL + + UR - - LU + + RU - -</strong></p><p>两角翻可以旋转一条棱上的两个轴: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image64.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>RU - - UR + + RU + + UR - - RU + + UR + + RU - - UR - - RU + + UR - - RU - - UR + +</strong></p><p><strong>第四步: 复原最后的单色块</strong></p><p>这里介绍一个两对换公式: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image65.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>UR - - RB + RU - - UR + + RU - RB - RU + UR + + RU + + UR - -</strong></p><p>将该公式中的一组对换取成同色块(通常是右侧面上两块同色), 可以很方便地复原最后的部分, 再通过叠加或是set up, 可以处理所有的情况. </p><p>如下图对换可以拆成沿虚线的对换: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image66.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>又如下图可以用角块三循环来set up: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image67.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>至此魔方复原. </p>"},"algs":[],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/star-pyraminx/en/image1.png","warningCount":2,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
